{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_05_02",
  "title": "井川葵 2話 新たな輝き",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ、{user}君\n仕事、取ってきてくれたんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ {user}.\nYou get me a work‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。これなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I did. But it's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2800.000000000001,
          "startTime": 9.2666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "……新作ジュエリーの広告モデル？　僕が？\nこれはまた、随分と攻めた仕事だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Modeling for a jewelry ad?\nThat's quite an unusual work‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2999998729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうかな？\nクールな葵にぴったりな仕事だと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think so?\nI think it's a perfect fit for cool and stylish you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも僕、ジュエリーなんて全然詳しくないよ？\n似合うとも思えないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't know anything about jewelry‚\nand I can't imagine it suits me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0373885247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "その点は、問題ない。詳しい必要はないし\nジュエリーが似合うことは、俺が保証する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not a problem. You don't need to know the details.\nI guarantee the jewelry will suit you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0666665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.0333332062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……\nその資料は……もしかして、当日着る衣装？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm…\nIs this outfit what I'll be wearing on the day of the shoot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.7333332062,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2700.0000000000027,
          "startTime": 40.7333332062
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、{user}君\n莉央の仕事と間違ってないよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}.\nAre you sure this isn't meant for Rio?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0333359864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ジュエリーに加えて、この衣装でモデルなんてさ\n僕が出来るのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Modeling jewelry in this outfit…\nCan I really do this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから随分弱腰じゃないか？\nこの前はあんなに仕事ほしそうだったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem a bit hesitant.\nWeren't you eager for work just the other day?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして君、煽ってきてる？\n別にやらないなんて一言も言ってないじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you teasing me?\nI haven't said I won't do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ。この仕事、引き受けるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ I'll take on this job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "君だって、この仕事がリズノワのためになるって\n思ったから、取ってきたんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ you believed it would benefit LizNoir‚\ndidn't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2333462579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "なら、それを信じるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ I'll trust your judgment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――広告の撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "--The day of the advertising shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "……一旦休憩だってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Let's take a break for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふぅ……やっと一息つける",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Finally‚ a breather.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、葵\nどうだ、モデルの仕事をやってみた感想は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ Aoi.\nHow was the modeling job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "正直に言うと、やっぱり落ち着かない\n撮られることは、そこまでじゃないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest‚ it still feels uneasy.\nBeing photographed isn't the issue‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり衣装とジュエリーがね\n似合っているのか分からなくて、ムズムズするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the outfit and the jewelry.\nI'm not sure if they suit me‚ and it's making me restless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "実際、君から見た感想はどう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's your objective opinion?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、バッチリいい感じだよ\n大人びた雰囲気も出ているしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You look great.\nYou exude a mature vibe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "……そっか……\n雰囲気は、一応、出てるんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I see…\nSo‚ you think the atmosphere is there…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "僕としては、一杯一杯過ぎてよく分からないからね\n客観的な意見は助かるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just that I'm not sure because I'm not used to it.\nI appreciate your objective opinion‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_02-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、普段のライブ以上に気力が奪われてる気がして\n思ってたより結構キツい仕事だな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "though. It's just that this work is more draining than I thought.\nIt's even tougher than our regular live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
